data.text:
Nintendo DS Video Game Complete.

Cases may have stickers and or residue on it from the stickers. Same goes with the cartridge itself.

This game comes complete with original case, instructions and game.

Game will be tested before shipping out.

Picture of actual item.

Shipping Info:

Rare games tend to be pricey, if you want an extra layer of protection like insurance or signature confirmation let me know. It will cost extra. I highly suggest signature confirmation, if you are home to sign for it. Oh, during covid times of what I have seen, they don't even make you sign but they hand it to you the person who opens the door. If you want a adult signature it will cost a tad more.

I'll will be using UPS (unless I run into problems making the label).

You can only select 1 choice from below; but you can add insurance + 1 option from below. Insurance up to $500 will only be a $3 Fee but it is covered by Shipsurance not UPS directly. Etsy has this too with USPS but I have not had to deal with Shipsurance, so I don't know how the steps are if you have to file a claim.

UPS will provide you with evidence of delivery in your choice of these options:

* Delivery Confirmation ($2 FEE): UPS will mail you a confirmation of delivery without a signature. Note: Similar information is available when you track your package online.

(I am not sure why one would want this or if it's more for you or me the seller).

* Signature Required ($6 FEE): UPS will obtain the recipient's signature or other electronic acknowledgement of receipt from the recipient when this option is selected and provide you with a printed copy. You may also view the recipient's signature or electronic acknowledgement of receipt online.

* Adult Signature Required ($7 FEE): UPS will obtain the adult recipient's signature and provide you with a printed copy. Adult recipients must be at least 21. You may also view the adult recipient's signature online.

Ok, so after making my very long listing ... I decided to play with the options section ... I am able to add the add ons onto this listing and you just have to select which one you want. If you don't want any extra protection just select "None".

If you want insurance + 1 choice ... I have abbreviated everything:

INS = Insurance

DC = Delivery Confirmation

SR = Signature Required

ASR = Adult Signature Required
